 And can we make everything smart?

07:46.620 --> 07:51.140
 It can range from the robot you have right now on the floor

07:51.140 --> 07:54.740
 to your refrigerator, to a camera,

07:54.740 --> 07:59.740
 to machines in manufacturing,

08:00.980 --> 08:03.500
 to retail, et cetera.

