 And as a result, we've seen enormous amount of progress

13:22.980 --> 13:26.300
 in getting spectrum allocated to 5G.

13:26.300 --> 13:29.380
 I think the real issue is the time that it takes

13:29.380 --> 13:31.660
 to build infrastructure.

