 over its pretty long history now,

21:23.940 --> 21:26.120
 a decade and a half maybe.

21:26.120 --> 21:27.320
 So it's constantly iterating.

21:27.320 --> 21:29.540
 There's constantly just like a turmoil of beautiful

21:29.540 --> 21:30.660
 innovations happening.

