 and this year it's Snapdragon 8Gen1.

21:40.100 --> 21:41.700
 It's a new naming scheme.

21:41.700 --> 21:44.820
 Okay, what's the sexiest, most beautiful idea

21:44.820 --> 21:47.060
 or concept to you about Snapdragon?

