 And then a video engine,

22:58.040 --> 23:01.660
 and a multimedia engine for every single application,

23:01.660 --> 23:03.780
 audio, everything.

23:03.780 --> 23:06.460
 So it's a single chip

23:06.460 --> 23:09.380
 that has every single computing technology

23:09.380 --> 23:10.620
 you need in the phone.

