 So if you want to build anything with 5G,

54:10.860 --> 54:13.500
 you need to get a license from Qualcomm

54:13.500 --> 54:16.860
 because it uses Qualcomm essential technology

54:16.860 --> 54:17.940
 as part of the standard.

